7. "git remote -v"   to view the configured remote Repository
8. "git remote add upstream https://github.com/Shahrul/testgit.git"    this is to add upstream 
    8.1 "git remote -v"   now should show additional entry for upstream
9. "git pull upstream master"   pull from the upstream master branch